msgctxt ""
"04000000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155388\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/sdatabase/04030000.xhp\">Form in Design Mode</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/sdatabase/04030000.xhp\">ແບບຟອມໃນໂໝດການອອກແບບ</link>"

#. jwRmr
#: 04000000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04000000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150504\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In design mode, the form is designed and the properties of the form and the controls contained in it are defined."
msgstr "ໃນໂໝດການອອກແບບ, ແບບຟອມຈະຖືກອອກແບບ ແລະ ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງແບບຟອມລວມທັງຕົວຄວບຄຸມຕ່າງໆທີ່ຢູ່ໃນນັ້ນຈະຖືກກຳນົດ."

#. qJXDP
#: 04000000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04000000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149784\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/main0213.xhp\">Sorting and Filtering Data</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/main0213.xhp\">ການຈັດລຽງ ແລະ ການກັ່ນຕອງຂໍ້ມູນ</link>"

#. 9s5BM
#: 04000000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04000000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151384\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You will find the sorting and filter functions in the toolbar when you open a form in user mode."
msgstr "ທ່ານຈະພົບຟັງຊັນການຈັດລຽງ ແລະ ການກັ່ນຕອງໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື ເມື່ອທ່ານເປີດແບບຟອມໃນໂໝດຜູ້ໃຊ້."

