"par_id3147088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Specify the settings for a dBASE database.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ກຳນົດການຕັ້ງຄ່າສຳລັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ dBASE.</ahelp>"

#. bSnXm
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To be able to define relations between tables, use JDBC or ODBC from within $[officename]."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດກຳນົດສາຍພົວພັນລະຫວ່າງຕາຕະລາງ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ JDBC ຫຼື ODBC ຈາກພາຍໃນ $[officename]."

#. irtxH
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Display inactive records"
msgstr "ສະແດງລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ງານ"

#. Y4AnV
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"dbaccess/ui/dbasepage/showDelRowsCheckbutton\">Displays all the records in a file, including those marked as deleted. If you select this check box, you cannot delete records.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"dbaccess/ui/dbasepage/showDelRowsCheckbutton\">ສະແດງທຸກໆລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນໃນໄຟລ໌, ລວມທັງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກໝາຍວ່າລຶບແລ້ວ. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກກ່ອງໝາຍນີ້, ທ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. 7vpRc
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3156023\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In dBASE format, deleted records remain in the file."
msgstr "ໃນຮູບແບບ dBASE, ລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກລຶບຈະຍັງຄົງຢູ່ໃນໄຟລ໌."

#. ZYefW
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151384\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To view any changes that you make to the database, close the connection to the database, and then reconnect the database."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເບິ່ງການປ່ຽນແປງໃດໆທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ເຮັດກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ປິດການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ແລ້ວເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ."

#. 5LBSi
#: 11030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11030000.xhp\n"
"par_id0904200811094971\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select the code conversion that you want to use to view the database in $[officename]. This does not affect the database.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກການແປງລະຫັດທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ເພື່ອເບິ່ງຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃນ $[officename]. ນີ້ຈະບໍ່ມີຜົນຕໍ່ຖານຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp>"

#. Gmun9
