#. BtQ2b
#: 11080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154288\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"sqltext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Opens a dialog where you can enter an SQL command for administering a database.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"sqltext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມໂຕ້ຕອບເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ສຳລັບການບໍລິຫານຖານຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້.</ahelp></variable>"

#. jhBMm
#: 11080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can only enter administration commands in this dialog, such as Grant, Create Table, or Drop Table, and not filter commands. The commands that you can enter depend on the data source, for example, dBASE can only run some of the SQL commands list here."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນສະເພາະຄຳສັ່ງການບໍລິຫານໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້, ເຊັ່ນ Grant, Create Table, ຫຼື Drop Table, ແລະ ບໍ່ແມ່ນຄຳສັ່ງການກັ່ນຕອງ. ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນໄດ້ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ, dBASE ສາມາດເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ພຽງບາງຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນລາຍຊື່ນີ້ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. xvNDZ
#: 11080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154860\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To run an SQL query for filtering data in the database, use the <link href=\"text/sdatabase/02010100.xhp\">Query Design View</link>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແລ່ນການສອບຖາມ SQL ສຳລັບການກັ່ນຕອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ <link href=\"text/sdatabase/02010100.xhp\">ມຸມມອງການອອກແບບການສອບຖາມ</link>."

#. Ck9G4
#: 11080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Command to execute"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ຈະປະຕິບັດ"

#. BHLbE
