msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147618\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"dbaccess/ui/directsqldialog/sql\">Enter the SQL administration command that you want to run.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"dbaccess/ui/directsqldialog/sql\">ປ້ອນຄຳສັ່ງການບໍລິຫານ SQL ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແລ່ນ.</ahelp>"

#. 5DFEP
#: 11080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"11080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153087\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, for a \"Bibliography\" data source, you can enter the following SQL command:"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ, ສຳລັບແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ \"Bibliography\", ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

