msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_id4572283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The availability of the following controls depends on the type of database:"
msgstr "ການມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານຂອງການຄວບຄຸມຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບປະເພດຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ:"

#. 8pnWD
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN10590\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use SQL92 naming constraints"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ກຳນົດການຕັ້ງຊື່ແບບ SQL92"

#. CZ3vk
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN10594\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Only allows characters that conform to the SQL92 naming convention in a name in a data source. All other characters are rejected. Each name must begin with a lowercase letter, an uppercase letter, or an underscore ( _ ). The remaining characters can be ASCII letters, numbers, and underscores.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ອະນຸຍາດສະເພາະຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັບຂໍ້ກຳນົດການຕັ້ງຊື່ SQL92 ໃນຊື່ຂອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຕົວອັກສອນອື່ນໆທັງໝົດຈະຖືກປະຕິເສດ. ແຕ່ລະຊື່ຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນພິມນ້ອຍ, ຕົວອັກສອນພິມໃຫຍ່, ຫຼື ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດກ້ອງ ( _ ). ຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ເຫຼືອສາມາດເປັນຕົວອັກສອນ ASCII, ຕົວເລກ, ແລະ ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດກ້ອງ.</ahelp>"

#. UDWZ7
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN1059E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Append the table alias name in SELECT statements"
msgstr "ຕື່ມຊື່ນາມແຝງຂອງຕາຕະລາງໃນຄຳສັ່ງ SELECT"

#. v2ZEZ
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN105A2\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Appends the alias to the table name in SELECT statements.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຕື່ມນາມແຝງໃສ່ຊື່ຕາຕະລາງໃນຄຳສັ່ງ SELECT.</ahelp>"

#. wHaBn
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN105907\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use keyword AS before table alias names"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຄຳສຳຄັນ AS ກ່ອນຊື່ນາມແຝງຂອງຕາຕະລາງ"

#. xEpbm
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN105947\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Some databases use the keyword \"AS\" between a name and its alias, while other databases use a whitespace. Enable this option to insert AS before the alias.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຖານຂໍ້ມູນບາງແຫ່ງໃຊ້ຄຳສຳຄັນ \"AS\" ລະຫວ່າງຊື່ ແລະ ນາມແຝງຂອງມັນ, ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຖານຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນໆໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ຫວ່າງ. ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອແຊກ AS ກ່ອນນາມແຝງ.</ahelp>"

#. 6kz2C
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN105A5\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use Outer Join syntax '{OJ }'"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໄວຍາກອນ Outer Join '{OJ }'"

#. 9PDve
#: dabaadvpropdat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabaadvpropdat.xhp\n"
"par_idN105A9\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Use escape sequences for outer joins. The syntax for this escape sequence is {oj outer-join}</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ໃຊ້ລຳດັບເອສເຄັບ (escape sequences) ສຳລັບ outer joins. ໄວຍາກອນສຳລັບລຳດັບເອສເຄັບນີ້ແມ່ນ {oj outer-join}</ahelp>"

#. xahKj
