"par_idN10645\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Enter an SQL statement that returns the last auto-incremented value for the primary key data field.</ahelp> For example:"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ປ້ອນຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ທີ່ຈະສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າທີ່ເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນອັດຕະໂນມັດລ່າສຸດສຳລັບເຂດຂໍ້ມູນກະແຈຫຼັກ.</ahelp> ຕົວຢ່າງ:"

