msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ກຳນົດຕົວເລືອກໃນການເຂົ້າເຖິງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#jdbc\">JDBC</link>.</ahelp>"

#. MAM5R
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10623\n"
"help.text"
msgid "JDBC Examples"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ JDBC"

#. FAkVF
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10627\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"productname\">You can use a JDBC driver class to connect to a JDBC database from %PRODUCTNAME</item>. The driver class is provided by the database manufacturer. Two examples of JDBC databases are Oracle and MySQL."
msgstr "<item type=\"productname\">ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຄລາດໄດຣເວີ JDBC ເພື່ອເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ JDBC ຈາກ %PRODUCTNAME</item>. ຄລາດໄດຣເວີແມ່ນສະໜອງໃຫ້ໂດຍຜູ້ຜະລິດຖານຂໍ້ມູນ. ສອງຕົວຢ່າງຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ JDBC ແມ່ນ Oracle ແລະ MySQL."

#. ehUZi
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN1062D\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The driver classes must be added to %PRODUCTNAME in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - %PRODUCTNAME - Advanced</menuitem>."
msgstr "ຄລາດໄດຣເວີຕ້ອງຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ຢູ່ທີ່ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄວາມມັກ (Preferences)</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - %PRODUCTNAME - ຂັ້ນສູງ</menuitem>."

#. KTrhC
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10634\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Oracle database"
msgstr "ຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Oracle"

#. Br2JC
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10638\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can use a JDBC driver to access an Oracle database from Solaris or Linux. To access the database from Windows, you need an ODBC driver."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດຣເວີ JDBC ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Oracle ຈາກ Solaris ຫຼື Linux. ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຖານຂໍ້ມູນຈາກ Windows, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໄດຣເວີ ODBC."

#. pei94
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN1064B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On UNIX, ensure that the Oracle database client is installed with JDBC support. The JDBC driver class for the Solaris Oracle client version 8.x is located in the <Oracle client>/product/jdbc/lib/classes111.zip directory. You can also download the latest version from the Oracle web site."
msgstr "ໃນ UNIX, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງໄຄລແອນ (client) ຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Oracle ດ້ວຍການຮອງຮັບ JDBC. ຄລາດໄດຣເວີ JDBC ສຳລັບ Oracle ໄຄລແອນ ເວີຊັນ 8.x ຂອງ Solaris ແມ່ນຕັ້ງຢູ່ໃນໂຟນເດີ <Oracle client>/product/jdbc/lib/classes111.zip. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດດາວໂຫຼດເວີຊັນຫຼ້າສຸດໄດ້ຈາກເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງ Oracle."

#. DifQh
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10661\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Data source URL</emph> box, enter the location of the Oracle database server. The syntax of the URL depends on the database type. See the documentation that came with the JDBC driver for more information."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງ <emph>URL ຂອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນທີ່ຕັ້ງຂອງເຊີເວີຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Oracle. ໄວຍາກອນຂອງ URL ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບປະເພດຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ. ເບິ່ງເອກະສານທີ່ມາກັບໄດຣເວີ JDBC ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. BBFrJ
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10668\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For an Oracle database, the syntax of the URL is:"
msgstr "ສຳລັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Oracle, ໄວຍາກອນຂອງ URL ແມ່ນ:"

#. 7tbob
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN1066B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "oracle:thin:@hostname:port:database_name"
msgstr "oracle:thin:@hostname:port:database_name"

#. RiDDR
#: dabawiz02jdbc.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dabawiz02jdbc.xhp\n"
"par_idN10674\n"
"help.text"
