"hd_id361540562942432\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"addfields\"><link href=\"text/sdatabase/rep_insertfield.xhp\">Add fields to report</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"addfields\"><link href=\"text/sdatabase/rep_insertfield.xhp\">ເພີ່ມຟິວເຂົ້າໃນລາຍງານ</link></variable>"

#. zFCzB
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id3587145\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">The Add Field window helps you to insert the table entries in the report.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ໜ້າຕ່າງເພີ່ມຟິວຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານໃນການແຊກລາຍການຕາຕະລາງເຂົ້າໃນລາຍງານ.</ahelp>"

#. dzGbq
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id4503921\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Add Field window is shown automatically when you have selected a table in the Contents box and leave that box."
msgstr "ໜ້າຕ່າງເພີ່ມຟິວຈະສະແດງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກຕາຕະລາງໃນກ່ອງເນື້ອຫາແລ້ວອອກຈາກກ່ອງນັ້ນ."

#. hQDBC
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id171540674707522\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">View - Add Field</item>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ມຸມມອງ - ເພີ່ມຟິວ</item>."

#. oEoAE
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id121540674874655\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the Add Field icon on the toolbar."
msgstr "ຄລິກໄອຄອນ ເພີ່ມຟິວ ເທິງແຖບເຄື່ອງມື."

#. e4BhF
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id991540674901837\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/lc_addfield.svg\" id=\"img_id621540674901837\" width=\"1.0cm\" height=\"1.0cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id491540674901837\">Add Field icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/lc_addfield.svg\" id=\"img_id621540674901837\" width=\"1.0cm\" height=\"1.0cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id491540674901837\">ໄອຄອນ ເພີ່ມຟິວ</alt></image>"

#. jYge5
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id121540664874655\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Add Field icon on the toolbar."
msgstr "ໄອຄອນ ເພີ່ມຟິວ ເທິງແຖບເຄື່ອງມື."

#. BqWBD
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id141540563922693\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the field in the Add Field dialog and click <emph>Insert</emph>. You can select multiple fields pressing the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> key while clicking on the fields name or using the Shift key while pressing the mouse button. Click <emph>Insert</emph> in the toolbar to add the fields to the report."
msgstr "ເລືອກຟິວໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບເພີ່ມຟິວ ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ແຊກ</emph>. ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຫຼາຍຟິວໄດ້ໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຄລິກຊື່ຟິວ ຫຼື ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ Shift ໃນຂະນະທີ່ກົດປຸ່ມເມົາສ໌. ຄລິກ <emph>ແຊກ</emph> ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືເພື່ອເພີ່ມຟິວເຂົ້າໃນລາຍງານ."

#. BGjjH
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id4051026\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drag and drop the field names one by one from the Add Field window into the Detail area of the report. Position the fields as you like. Use the icons in the toolbars to align the fields."
msgstr "ລາກ ແລະ ວາງຊື່ຟິວເທື່ອລະອັນຈາກໜ້າຕ່າງເພີ່ມຟິວເຂົ້າໃນພື້ນທີ່ລາຍລະອຽດຂອງລາຍງານ. ຈັດວາງຕຳແໜ່ງຟິວຕາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ. ໃຊ້ໄອຄອນໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືເພື່ອຈັດລຽງຟິວ."

#. Hk568
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id3397320\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is not possible to overlap the fields. If you drop a table field on the Detail area, then a label and a text box are inserted."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດວາງຟິວຊ້ອນທັບກັນໄດ້. ຖ້າທ່ານວາງຟິວຕາຕະລາງລົງໃນພື້ນທີ່ລາຍລະອຽດ, ປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກແຊກເຂົ້າມາ."

#. N9RC7
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id3059785\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also insert text that should be the same on every page of the report. Click the Label Field icon, then drag a rectangle in the Page Header or Page Footer area. Edit the Label property to show the text you want."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດແຊກຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຄວນຈະຄືກັນໃນທຸກໆໜ້າຂອງລາຍງານໄດ້. ຄລິກໄອຄອນ ຟິວປ້າຍຊື່, ແລ້ວລາກເປັນຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກໃນພື້ນທີ່ຫົວໜ້າ ຫຼື ທ້າຍໜ້າ. ແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດປ້າຍຊື່ເພື່ອສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ."

#. yombL
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id991540874901837\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id5605334\" src=\"cmd/lc_addfield.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\" localize=\"true\"><alt id=\"alt_id5605334\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id5605334\" src=\"cmd/lc_addfield.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\" localize=\"true\"><alt id=\"alt_id5605334\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. pSksR
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"par_id121542664874655\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Add Label Field icon on the toolbar."
msgstr "ໄອຄອນ ເພີ່ມຟິວປ້າຍຊື່ ເທິງແຖບເຄື່ອງມື."

#. VjpkA
#: rep_insertfield.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rep_insertfield.xhp\n"
"hd_id251540563929787\n"
