#. rBE4D
#: tablewizard00.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tablewizard00.xhp\n"
"par_idN1055C\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">The Table Wizard helps you to create a database table.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຕາຕະລາງ ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສ້າງຕາຕະລາງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp>"

#. oP89L
