#. GgEVx
#: tablewizard01.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tablewizard01.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Table Wizard - Select Fields"
msgstr "ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຕາຕະລາງ - ເລືອກເຂດຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. ZFKJc
#: tablewizard01.xhp
