"tablewizard01.xhp\n"
"par_idN10546\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/sdatabase/tablewizard01.xhp\">Table Wizard - Select Fields</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/sdatabase/tablewizard01.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຕາຕະລາງ - ເລືອກເຂດຂໍ້ມູນ</link>"

#. 4HLFY
#: tablewizard01.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tablewizard01.xhp\n"
"par_idN10556\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select fields from the provided sample tables as a starting point to create your own table."
msgstr "ເລືອກເຂດຂໍ້ມູນຈາກຕາຕະລາງຕົວຢ່າງທີ່ໃຫ້ມາ ເພື່ອເປັນຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃນການສ້າງຕາຕະລາງຂອງທ່ານເອງ."

#. csKoV
#: tablewizard01.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tablewizard01.xhp\n"
"par_idN10559\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Business"
